#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/valkey.rst:7
msgid ""
"Valkey is an open source (BSD) high-performance key/value datastore and "
"is a supported option for remote KV Cache offloading in LMCache. Some "
"other remote backends are :doc:`Mooncake <./mooncake>`, :doc:`Redis "
"<./redis>`, and :doc:`InfiniStore <./infinistore>`."
msgstr "Valkey 是一个开源（BSD）高性能键值数据存储，并且是 LMCache 中支持的远程 KV Cache 卸载选项之一。其他一些远程后端包括 :doc:`Mooncake <./mooncake>`、:doc:`Redis <./redis>` 和 :doc:`InfiniStore <./infinistore>`。"

